description:
A free tool to convert WBFS file to Wii game ISO files.

WBFS to ISO is a free game tool for all Wii users, it can convert WBFS file to Wii game ISO files, it is simple and easy to use, the WBFS is the abbreviation for Wii backup file system, one WBFS file always contains one full Wii game, this free tool can help you easily to convert your WBFS files to Wii game ISO file format.
